| style="background:#ddd; color:#000;" | [[Перепис населення США (2010)|2010]]<ref name=autogenerated2>{{cite web|url=http://2010.census.gov/2010census/data/apportionment-pop-text.php|title=Resident Population Data|date=2010-12-21|publisher=United States Census Bureau|accessdate=2010-12-21|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/619lRoKht|archivedate=2011-08-23}}</ref> || 309,1
