=== Мови США ===
{|class="infobox" style="font-size: 90%; border: 1px solid #999; float: right; margin-left: 1em; width: 200px;"
|- style="background:#f5f5f5;"
!colspan="2"|Мови (2007)<ref name="USCB Lang">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/compendia/statab/2010/tables/ref>{{cite web|url=http://atvb.ahajournals.org/cgi/content/full/25/12/2451#R3-101329|title=Fast Food, Central Nervous System Insulin Resistance, and Obesity|year=2005|accessdate=2007-06-17|work=[[Arteriosclerosis, Thrombosis, and Vascular Biology]]|publisher=American Heart Association|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/6HZLdt56D|archivedate=2013-06-22}}10s0053.pdf|publisher=U.S. Census Bureau|work=Statistical Abstract of the United States 2010|title=Table 53—Languages Spoken at Home by Language: 2007|accessdate=2009-09-21}}</ref>
